item.title: Starting point
item.description: This is the my first entry in this blog, just to mark the starting point. I am writing this in a train while returning “home” and at this moment, I don’t know how the blog will develop. I have some ideas of what I want to share here, but not a concrete plan. Perhaps this will only last a few months until I drop it like many other projects. In any case, what I want to show here are:
